	<a href="http://www.cs.indiana.edu/mit.research.how.to/mit.research.how.to.html">How To Do Research In the MIT AI Lab</a>.&nbsp; A paper edited by David Chapman and now available on the web.&nbsp; Part of it is about being a graduate student, other parts are specific to AI, as it was envisioned in 1987-1988.<br>
