	<div class="posts">
	<a name="90530985">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<h1>Software Development</h1><h2>Programming Languages</h2><h3>The Java 2 programming language</h3><a href="http://java.sun.com/docs/books/jls/">The Java Language Specification</a>.&nbsp; The main page for the specification, with the different formats you can obtain it in, including the print edition.  The PDF is 4.4MB and a ZIP of the HTML format is one-tenth that.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#90530985">Tuesday, March 11, 2003</a></span></div>
<br>
  <!-- 2002-11-08 Change date format to yyyy-mm-dd and bookmark it 
                2002-11-09 Tune the color and make a purplized link out of it -->
	

	<div class="posts">
	<a name="90530882">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://java.sun.com/docs/books/jls/second_edition/html/j.title.doc.html">The Java Language Specification, ed.2</a>.&nbsp; OK, the title page.&nbsp; The earlier link is to the Table of Content.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#90530882">Tuesday, March 11, 2003</a></span></div>
<br>
  <!-- 2002-11-08 Change date format to yyyy-mm-dd and bookmark it 
                2002-11-09 Tune the color and make a purplized link out of it -->
	

