	<div class="posts">
	<a name="90414175">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.cooper.com/index.asp">Cooper</a>.&nbsp; The web site of Alan Cooper's firm.&nbsp; The site illustrates some of the Interaction Design principles, and I notice that there is an expanding customer list, case studies, and certification processes.&nbsp; Fascinating to me.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#90414175">Sunday, March 09, 2003</a></span></div>
